  "markup": "\u003Cp class=\u0022p1\u0022\u003EIn this webinar, we explore the cervical spine and the common pathologies for it in the clinical practice. You\u0027ll also learn how to effectively treat a wide variety of conditions utilizing the Priority Principle and Super Pulsed Laser Technology.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\u0022p1\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg height=\u0022505\u0022 alt=\u0022January 2012 LTU Webinar\u0022 width=\u0022590\u0022 src=\u0022~/media/C0C2E0FFA2F64F42A2F092E8715BA4BA.ashx\u0022 /\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
